    <item>
      <title>美国国债结束四天抛售，亚洲股市下跌：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国国债价格上涨，结束了连续四天的抛售潮。抛售潮是由对通胀持续上涨的担忧引发的，而当选总统唐纳德·特朗普的财政刺激计划可能会加剧通胀上涨的局面。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 22:28:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>520 亿美元的损失将使洛杉矶火灾成为美国最严重的灾难之一</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/los-angeles-fires-to-top-50-billion-in-damage-accuweather-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[对洛杉矶大火所造成的经济影响的初步估计显示，该火灾是美国有史以来损失最惨重的自然灾害之一，也可能是美国有史以来损失最惨重的山林火灾。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/los-angeles-fires-to-top-50-billion-in-damage-accuweather-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 21:24:24 GMT</pubDate>
